extends ./layout.pug

block content
    .all
        section.main-section
            .wrap
                .tcont
                    .tcell
                        .main-box(data-animate='fadeIn', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0', data-offset='90%')
                            h2.title(data-animate='fadeInRight', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0', data-offset='90%')
                                | TRAVEL
                                | ROUTE
                            h1.text(data-animate='fadeInRight', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0.2s', data-offset='90%')
                                | Your
                                | Personal Travel Guide
                                br
                                |  & Free Itinerary Planner
                            a.btn(href='#', data-animate='fadeInRight', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0.4s', data-offset='90%') Choose Your Adventure
                .hand(data-animate='fadeIn', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0', data-offset='90%')
        section.section.filled-section.what-section
            .wrap
                .what-is
                    .inner
                        h2(data-animate='fadeInUp', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0', data-offset='90%')
                            | What is Travel
                            | Route?
                        .text(data-animate='fadeInUp', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0', data-offset='90%')
                            | Here
                            | at Travel Route we have one mission - worry free adventures of a lifetime, for less. We believe that the world
                            | belongs to travel enthusiasts and explorers, so go out and immerse yourself in the culture, cuisine and wonders
                            | of your dream destination, while we take care of all the nitty gritty details ahead of time. All you have to do
                            | is follow. Are you in?
        section.section.how-section
            .wrap
                h1(data-animate='fadeInUp', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0', data-offset='90%') How it Works
                .subtitle(data-animate='fadeInUp', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0', data-offset='90%')
                    | In
                    | three simpe steps
                .how-boxes
                    .col
                        .box(data-animate='fadeInUp', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0', data-offset='90%')
                            .number 1
                            h4 Get inspired
                            .text
                                | Our captivating, ready-to-use itineraries and travel plans cater to every taste and style of travel. Whether
                                | you are planning your next romantic getaway, meeting the family overseas, looking to hike the Amalfi coast or
                                | travelling with children, simply pick the options you would like and let our itinerary magic tool build the
                                | perfect adventure. Made with love, just for you.
                    .col
                        .box(data-animate='fadeInUp', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0.15s', data-offset='90%')
                            .number 2
                            h4 Make it your own
                            .text
                                | We believe that each trip should be special, and as such - we want to make it all about you. With Travel Route,
                                | you can edit any detail of the itinerary of your choice. From the places you visit and the experiences that
                                | await to the time and date of your grand adventure. You can even combine multiple different itineraries
                                | together to make your next adventure just right. Ready to roll? Book your adventure, right from the itinerary
                                | and get ready to explore.
                    .col
                        .box(data-animate='fadeInUp', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0.3s', data-offset='90%')
                            .number 3
                            h4 Go travel
                            .text
                                | Pack your bags, make sure your stove is off, grab your boarding passes and let's set out on an epic adventure.
                                | Travel Route will be by your side to guide you the entire time! A ccess your itineraries online, save them to
                                | your personal devices or print them for convenient, organized travel. So, what are you waiting for? A worry
                                | free epic trip of a lifetime awaits you!
        section.section.filled-section.adv-section
            .wrap
                .advant-block
                    .image
                    .text
                        h2(data-animate='fadeInUp', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0', data-offset='90%') Our Advantages
                        ul.mark-list
                            li(data-animate='fadeIn', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0', data-offset='90%')
                                | Travel Route is
                                | absolutely free and easy to use.
                            li(data-animate='fadeIn', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0.1s', data-offset='90%')
                                | We offer an
                                | extensive collection of ready-to-use travel plans, carefully hand-crafted by our experts just for you.
                            li(data-animate='fadeIn', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0.2s', data-offset='90%')
                                | Our
                                | itineraries are created by real people not by machines.
                            li(data-animate='fadeIn', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0.3s', data-offset='90%')
                                | We
                                | collaborate with local companies to make your experience truly authentic.
                            li(data-animate='fadeIn', data-init='hidden', data-duration='1s', data-delay='0.4s', data-offset='90%')
                                | All trips
                                | are planned down to the smallest details, from working hours and recommended visit duration to transport and
                                | routes.
